sustainability science fellowship at harvard university the leopold leadership program skip to main content search this site the leopold leadership program about fellows news fellowship information resources login fellowships positions early career environmental scholars new fellowships new positions sustainability science fellowship at harvard university sustainability science fellowship at harvard university academic level phd postdoctoral focus sustainability awards open to all duration semester or less notes the sustainability science program at harvard university's center for international development offers doctoral post doctoral and mid career fellowships in sustainability science the program seeks to facilitate the design implementation and evaluation of effective interventions that promote sustainable development to that end we seek to advance scientific understanding of human environment systems to improve linkages between relevant research and innovation communities on the one hand and relevant policy and management communities on the other and more broadly to build capacity for linking knowledge with action to promote sustainability deadline info applications are due in december each year 2012 leopold leadership program the stanford woods institute for the environment stanford university stanford ca 94305
